com.diogonunes.jcdp.bw.api

Class AbstractPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diogonunes.jcdp.bw.api.AbstractPrinter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPrinter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractColoredPrinter, TerminalPrinter

    public abstract class AbstractPrinter
extends Object
implements IPrinter
    This class is a template of a Printer, hence it contains what is common to each Printer implementation offered by the library. Each Printer of this package should extend this class and thus implement Printer interface.
